# `npm run dev` targets the ISOLATED DEV backend (bobs-*-dev tables) — never prod data.
# Connect/CCP is shared with prod (no separate dev Connect instance).
# To point local dev at prod instead, set VITE_API_URL in .env.local (it overrides this file).
